## Why This Is Asked

Tests practical secret management and runtime retrieval in GCP.

## Key Concepts

- Secret Manager rotation, Cloud Scheduler, Pub/Sub, Cloud Run IAM bindings, request-time secret fetch.

## Code Example

```javascript
// Runtime fetch of Secret Manager secret in Cloud Run (Node.js)
const {SecretManagerServiceClient} = require('@google-cloud/secret-manager');
const client = new SecretManagerServiceClient();
async function getApiKey() {
  const name = 'projects/PROJECT/secrets/API_KEY/versions/latest';
  const [version] = await client.accessSecretVersion({name});
  const apiKey = version.payload.data.toString('utf8');
  return apiKey;
}
```

## Follow-up Questions

- How would you test failure of rotation propagation?
- How would you handle secret versioning and rollback?

